<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē munibiṁdupāvakadharā saṁkhyānvitē kārttikē śu
<lb n="2" break="no"/>jlē viṣṇutithau sudhākaradinē śrīsiṁhyaśailaprabhōḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dugdhānnārtthama
<lb n="3" break="no"/>dāt gavāṁ pratidinaṁ paṁ<unclear>cā</unclear>śataṁ vai śubhāṁ mālāṁ ca prabhurayya
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dēvanṛpatiḥ svābhīṣṭasaṁsiddhayē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśakavarṣaṁbulu 1307 gunē
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṁṭi kārttika śukla dvādaśiyu sōmavāramunāṁḍu Ōrugaṁṭi haritagō
<lb n="6" break="no"/>trajuṁḍaina Annadēvarāju koḍuku Ayyadēvarāju tanaku manōra<unclear>tha</unclear>
<lb n="7" break="no"/>siddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhyanāthuniki ṟēpaṭi dhūpā<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>sarana pāyassamu 
<lb n="8"/>Āragiṁpuṭaku peṭṭina mōdālu 50 I pālu tecci pōyanu kilā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ri nāraṇanāyaniki jītamu vuṭeṁḍu kṣētramu duttaḍaceṟuvu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>lōnu koni peṭṭenu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> I Avasaranana nityamunnu Oka doṁḍavanamāla te
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ccipeṭṭanu bisāḷibhīmaniki reṁḍu kuṁcālu prasādamu padi māḍalaku 10
<lb n="12"/>ṭhāvupaṭi peṭiri tōṁṭagaṭlu <unclear>reṁ</unclear>ḍu koni peṭitimi Ī dharmu Ācaṁdrārkasthā
<lb n="13" break="no"/>yigānu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrī śrī śrī
</p>

